s: The John Prine Anthology]]''\n| \u2014\n| [[Rhino Records|Rhino]]\n|-\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+John Prine guest singles\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Single\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Artist\n!| Peak positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| [[Hot Country Songs|US Country]]\n|-\n| 1992\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''Sweet Suzanne''\n| Buzzin' Cousins\n| 68\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''[[Falling from Grace (film)|Falling from Grace]]'' soundtrack\n|-\n| 2013\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''Yes We Will''\n| [[Maria Doyle Kennedy]]\n| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''Sing'' \n|-\n| 2020\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''Memories''\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Swamp Dogg]]\n| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"rowspan=\"2\"| ''Sorry You Couldn't Make It'' \n|-\n| 2020\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| ''Please Let Me Go Around Again''\n| \u2013\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+John Prine video albums\n|-\n!| Year\n!| Title\n!| Label\n|-\n| 2001\n| ''[[John Prine - Live from Sessions at West 54th|John Prine \u2013 Live from Sessions at West 54th]]''\n| [[Oh Boy Records]] Music Video\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|+John Prine music videos\n|-\n! Year\n! style=\"width:12em;\"| Video\n! Director\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 1992\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Picture Show''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/383897/picture-show.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine : Picture Show|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917084824/http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/383897/picture-show.jhtml|archive-date=September 17, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Jim Shea\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Sweet Suzanne'' <small>(Buzzin' Cousins)\n| [[Marty Callner]]\n|-\n| 1993\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Speed of the Sound of Loneliness'' {{small|(featuring [[Nanci Griffith]])}}\n| [[Rocky Schenck]]\n|-\n| 1995\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Ain't Hurtin' Nobody''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/103394/aint-hurtin-nobody.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine : Ain't Hurtin' Nobody|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917081451/http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/103394/aint-hurtin-nobody.jhtml|archive-date=September 17, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Jim Shea\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Fish and Whistle (Lyric Video)''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WNuuBfWFYvQ|title=John Prine \u2013 Fish and Whistle (Lyric Video)|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301215521/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WNuuBfWFYvQ|archive-date=March 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Northman Creative\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| ''I'm Telling You''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/1546089/im-telling-you-feat-holly-williams.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine, Holly Williams : I'm Telling You (feat. Holly Williams)|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917082236/http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/1546089/im-telling-you-feat-holly-williams.jhtml|archive-date=September 17, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><br />{{small|(featuring [[Holly Williams]])}}\n| Joshua Britt and Neilson Hubbard\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Color of the Blues'' featuring Susan Tedeschi<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAYoWePzQ2c|title=John Prine \u2013 Color of the Blues featuring Susan Tedeschi|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605150156/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAYoWePzQ2c|archive-date=June 5, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Joshua Britt and Neilson Hubbard\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Sweet Revenge''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube