e#Monthly awards|October 2011]]<ref name=PremProfile/>\n*[[Italian Football Hall of Fame]]: 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/27-10-2015/hall-of-fame-vialli-mancini-facchetti-ronaldo-herrera-agnelli-tardelli-ferlaino-130676725232.shtml|title=Hall of fame, 10 new entry: con Vialli e Mancini anche Facchetti e Ronaldo|trans-title=Hall of fame, 10 new entries: with Vialli and Mancini also Facchetti and Ronaldo|publisher=La Gazzetta dello Sport|language=Italian|date=27 October 2015|accessdate=27 October 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Enzo Bearzot Award]]: 2019<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/sport/calcio/2019/04/04/a-mancini-il-premio-bearzot-2019_69b67d27-1eaf-4269-bc8a-abaad455ecef.html|title=A Mancini il premio Bearzot 2019|publisher=Ansa.it|date=4 April 2019|language=italian}}</ref>\n{{col-end}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[List of English football championship-winning managers]]\n\n==Notes==\n<references group=\"nb\" />\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{Instagram|mrmancini10}}\n*[http://www.goal.com/en-gb/people/italy/170/roberto-mancini Roberto Mancini] at Goal.com {{dead link|date=February 2020}}\n*{{Webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302140705/http://www.mcfc.co.uk/Players/Management/Roberto-Mancini |title=Roberto Mancini at Mcfc.co.uk }}\n*{{Soccerbase manager|1709}}\n*[https://www.tuttocalciatori.net/index.php?mod=chp&par=22 Roberto Mancini] at Tuttocalciatori.net {{in lang|it}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ach}}\n{{s-bef|before= [[Carlo Ancelotti]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of FA Cup winning managers|FA Cup<br />Winning Manager]]|years=[[2010\u201311 FA Cup|2010\u201311]]}}\n{{s-aft|after= [[Roberto Di Matteo]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before= [[Alex Ferguson]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Premier League]]<br />Winning Manager|years=[[2011\u201312 Premier League|2011\u201312]]}}\n{{s-aft|after= [[Alex Ferguson]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Current managers of UEFA national teams}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n| title = Italy squads\n